Package: retrieve-omnipath-app
Type: Package
Title: A Shiny Application for Gene Interaction Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Elena Eyre-Sánchez
Maintainer: Elena Eyre-Sánchez <elenueyre@yahoo.es>
Description: This package provides a Shiny application that allows users to analyze gene interactions using data from the Omnipath database. Users can select source and target gene symbols from a provided list and visualize their interactions.
